.Dd March 28, 2026
.Dt GALE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm gale
.Nd fast, isolated package management for developers
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar command
.Op Ar args ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
installs CLI tools and runtimes into isolated,
versioned directories.
Projects get per-directory environments that activate
automatically on
.Xr cd 1
via
.Xr direnv 1 .
.Pp
Packages are declared in
.Pa gale.toml
and installed from recipes in a federated registry.
Prebuilt binaries are pulled from GHCR when available;
otherwise packages are built from source.
.Sh COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width "create-recipe" -compact
.It Cm install Ar pkg Ns Op @ Ns Ar ver
Install a package.
.It Cm remove Ar pkg
Remove a package.
.It Cm add Ar pkg ...
Add packages to
.Pa gale.toml
without installing.
.It Cm sync
Install all packages in
.Pa gale.toml .
.It Cm update Op Ar pkg ...
Update packages to the latest version.
.It Cm list
List packages in
.Pa gale.toml .
.It Cm env
Print
.Ev PATH
export for the current scope.
.It Cm init
Bootstrap a project with
.Pa gale.toml
and
.Pa .envrc .
.It Cm build Ar recipe.toml
Build a recipe from source.
.It Cm lint Ar recipe.toml ...
Validate recipe files.
.It Cm search Ar query
Search for packages.
.It Cm shell
Open a shell with the project environment.
.It Cm run Ar cmd
Run a command in the project environment.
.It Cm hook direnv
Print
.Fn use_gale
function for direnvrc.
.It Cm import homebrew Ar name
Import a Homebrew formula as a recipe.
.El
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Bl -tag -width "MANPATH"
.It Ev PATH
Add
.Pa ~/.gale/current/bin
to use globally installed packages.
.It Ev MANPATH
Add
.Pa ~/.gale/current/man
to read man pages for installed packages.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "~/.gale/gale.toml"
.It Pa ~/.gale/gale.toml
Global package declarations.
.It Pa ~/.gale/config.toml
Application settings (registry URL, AI config).
.It Pa ~/.gale/pkg/
Package store.
One directory per package per version.
.It Pa ~/.gale/current/
Symlink to the active generation directory.
.It Pa gale.toml
Project package declarations.
.It Pa .envrc
Direnv integration file created by
.Cm init .
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr direnv 1
.Sh AUTHORS
.An Travis Cole Aq Mt kelp@plek.org
